(Fourth Department,

July, 1974)

(July 5, 1974) Charles Kwiatkowski et al., Respondents, v. Town of Olean, Appellant.

Judgment unanimously affirmed, with costs, on-the opinion of Supreme Court, Cattaraugus County, Doerr, J. (Appeal from judgment of Cattaraugus Trial Term in action for injunction.) Present — Marsh, P. J., Witmer, Mahoney, Goldman and Del Yecchio, JJ.
